        <mxCell id="caption" value="The web app and the MCP server both rely on one shared Python core. Normal requests go Browser → Frontend → FastAPI → shared MCP logic → cluster or AI services, while SSH and MCP are optional alternate entry paths." style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=18;fontColor=#0F172A;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1">
